WEBVTT

00:00:07.414 --> 00:00:11.222
[metal scraping]

00:00:19.038 --> 00:00:20.040
- [gasps]

00:00:20.073 --> 00:00:21.677
Lord Tokito!

00:00:24.315 --> 00:00:27.421
- Don't underestimate me,
you damn brat!

00:00:30.861 --> 00:00:32.866
<i>["Kizuna no Kiseki" playing]</i>

00:00:32.899 --> 00:00:40.080
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:02:02.913 --> 00:02:04.916
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:02:08.891 --> 00:02:10.895
<i>[soft music]</i>

00:02:12.231 --> 00:02:15.036
- Hey, I'm not
underestimating you.

00:02:15.070 --> 00:02:16.874
I'm merely stating a fact.

00:02:16.907 --> 00:02:20.447
Getting beheaded by me is
just inevitable at this point.

00:02:20.481 --> 00:02:23.053
After all, for whatever reason,

00:02:23.086 --> 00:02:25.290
I'm really
in the zone right now.

00:02:26.192 --> 00:02:27.629
I wonder why.

00:02:27.662 --> 00:02:30.902
- How dare you speak to me
so disrespectfully,

00:02:30.936 --> 00:02:32.437
you miserable brat!

00:02:32.471 --> 00:02:34.442
As if someone
who's only lived a decade

00:02:34.475 --> 00:02:36.713
could ever hope to behead me!

00:02:40.721 --> 00:02:43.995
- I might be young, but I
despise everything about you,

00:02:44.028 --> 00:02:46.032
so I'm sure I'll find a way.

00:02:46.066 --> 00:02:48.937
From the way you look and talk,

00:02:48.971 --> 00:02:50.808
everything about you is creepy.

00:02:50.842 --> 00:02:54.281
- You simply can't appreciate
my beauty, my grace,

00:02:54.315 --> 00:02:55.952
or my elegance,

00:02:55.985 --> 00:02:57.388
because an imbecile like you

00:02:57.421 --> 00:03:01.196
is too uneducated and poor
to comprehend it!

00:03:01.229 --> 00:03:03.333
The same way a dung beetle
couldn't read a book

00:03:03.366 --> 00:03:05.203
if its life depended on it!

00:03:05.237 --> 00:03:06.741
- Now that you mention it,

00:03:06.774 --> 00:03:08.945
you do sort of look
like a dung beetle.

00:03:08.978 --> 00:03:10.714
- You're the dung battle,
damn it!

00:03:10.748 --> 00:03:12.451
Look at you
with your short limbs

00:03:12.485 --> 00:03:14.421
and that small, pathetic blade!

00:03:14.455 --> 00:03:16.927
You couldn't reach my neck
even if you tried!

00:03:16.961 --> 00:03:18.129
- Strange.

00:03:18.163 --> 00:03:20.702
If I'm not mistaken,
I did earlier.

00:03:20.735 --> 00:03:21.603
And unless I'm blind,

00:03:21.636 --> 00:03:23.740
your limbs
are shorter than mine.

00:03:23.774 --> 00:03:25.243
Oh, I get it now.

00:03:25.277 --> 00:03:27.950
You were just thinking
out loud about yourself.

00:03:27.983 --> 00:03:29.520
I'm sorry I interrupted.

00:03:29.553 --> 00:03:31.222
- Hyo, hyo!

00:03:31.255 --> 00:03:33.360
My, what a childish insult.

00:03:33.393 --> 00:03:34.662
Don't tell me you really thought

00:03:34.696 --> 00:03:36.633
that would be enough
to fluster me!

00:03:36.667 --> 00:03:39.171
I can see now
how desperate you are to win.

00:03:39.204 --> 00:03:41.543
What a sad sight to look upon.

00:03:41.577 --> 00:03:43.246
- Mm. Hmm.

00:03:43.279 --> 00:03:45.083
- Hyeh, hyeh!

00:03:45.116 --> 00:03:46.252
What's wrong?

00:03:46.285 --> 00:03:48.791
- It's really bugging me.

00:03:48.824 --> 00:03:50.327
That odd vase of yours,

00:03:50.361 --> 00:03:51.964
why is it misshapen?

00:03:51.997 --> 00:03:54.435
It's not symmetrical, is it?

00:03:56.072 --> 00:03:58.109
What a sad sight to look upon.

00:03:58.142 --> 00:03:59.145
- [gasps]

00:03:59.178 --> 00:04:01.081
How dare you critique my art

00:04:01.115 --> 00:04:03.954
with those
rotten eyeballs of yours!

00:04:03.988 --> 00:04:07.161
My vase is perfect!

00:04:07.194 --> 00:04:10.935
And certainly not misshapen!

00:04:10.968 --> 00:04:12.973
Blood Demon Art...

00:04:13.006 --> 00:04:14.208
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:04:14.241 --> 00:04:17.148
Ten Thousand Gliding Slime Fish!

00:04:17.181 --> 00:04:19.218
Once my 10,000 assassins

00:04:19.251 --> 00:04:21.389
are finished picking you clean
to the bone,

00:04:21.423 --> 00:04:24.329
I'll make you
into one of my beloved works!

00:04:24.362 --> 00:04:25.798
<i>- Mist Breathing...</i>

00:04:29.806 --> 00:04:33.346
<i>Sixth Form:
Lunar Dispersing Mist.</i>

00:04:38.824 --> 00:04:42.364
<i>- What?!
He slashed them all at once?!</i>

00:04:42.397 --> 00:04:44.769
<i>His speed and attack range
have increased!</i>

00:04:44.803 --> 00:04:48.310
<i>Why isn't my poison
having an effect on him?!</i>

00:04:48.343 --> 00:04:49.913
<i>I didn't expect this.</i>

00:04:49.946 --> 00:04:52.552
<i>Regardless,
I have nothing to worry about.</i>

00:04:52.585 --> 00:04:54.589
<i>You've dealt
with the immediate threat,</i>

00:04:54.622 --> 00:04:56.292
<i>but before those fish
turn to dust,</i>

00:04:56.325 --> 00:04:58.463
<i>they'll disperse more poison!</i>

00:04:58.497 --> 00:05:00.935
<i>And since it's
transdermal poison they release,</i>

00:05:00.968 --> 00:05:03.808
<i>it can also be absorbed
through the skin!</i>

00:05:03.841 --> 00:05:06.613
<i>Get hit with that,
and you're finished.</i>

00:05:06.646 --> 00:05:10.053
<i>- Mist Breathing Third Form...</i>

00:05:10.087 --> 00:05:11.957
<i>Scattering Mist Splash!</i>

00:05:11.990 --> 00:05:18.637
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:05:18.671 --> 00:05:20.073
<i>- What?!</i>

00:05:20.106 --> 00:05:23.881
<i>He blasted them all away
with just that one swing?!</i>

00:05:23.914 --> 00:05:25.383
[gasps]

00:05:28.022 --> 00:05:29.792
<i>- You can shed your skin.</i>

00:05:33.767 --> 00:05:36.472
You're proving to be
a real pain in the butt.

00:05:36.507 --> 00:05:39.813
Stop wasting my time hiding
in trees, and just fight me.

00:05:39.846 --> 00:05:42.150
- Hyo, hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:05:42.184 --> 00:05:43.353
Prepare yourself,

00:05:43.386 --> 00:05:46.059
for you're about
to witness my true form!

00:05:46.092 --> 00:05:47.061
- Go on.

00:05:47.094 --> 00:05:49.064
- [chuckles]

00:05:49.097 --> 00:05:52.839
Only two people before you
have seen me in this state.

00:05:52.873 --> 00:05:54.107
- Really? That many?

00:05:54.141 --> 00:05:55.276
- Shut up!

00:05:55.310 --> 00:05:56.913
No one's lived
to tell the tale

00:05:56.947 --> 00:05:59.753
once I've started
taking things seriously!

00:05:59.786 --> 00:06:01.656
- How amazing.

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:05.497
- Shut your mouth,
you dimwitted brat!

00:06:05.531 --> 00:06:08.236
I'll have you know
my translucent scales

00:06:08.270 --> 00:06:10.808
are harder and stronger
than diamonds.

00:06:10.842 --> 00:06:13.647
I kneaded each one
inside my vase!

00:06:13.681 --> 00:06:17.688
Behold my artistry
in its perfect, beautiful form!

00:06:17.722 --> 00:06:19.759
Bow down before me in awe!

00:06:23.099 --> 00:06:25.003
[chuckles]

00:06:26.005 --> 00:06:27.508
Um...

00:06:29.813 --> 00:06:32.184
Say something,
you worthless puppet!

00:06:32.218 --> 00:06:33.921
Quit playing dumb with me!

00:06:33.954 --> 00:06:36.325
You really know how to rub
someone the wrong way,

00:06:36.359 --> 00:06:37.562
don't you, brat?!

00:06:37.595 --> 00:06:41.135
- But you just told me
to shut my mouth earlier.

00:06:41.169 --> 00:06:42.137
Besides...

00:06:43.273 --> 00:06:45.076
it didn't really warrant
a reaction.

00:06:51.221 --> 00:06:53.092
<i>[soft music]</i>

00:06:53.125 --> 00:06:54.996
[liquid flows]

00:06:58.002 --> 00:07:00.006
[laughs]

00:07:00.875 --> 00:07:02.444
- Hold on.
Didn't you just tell me

00:07:02.478 --> 00:07:04.315
not to go hiding in trees?

00:07:04.348 --> 00:07:06.820
You're proving to be
a pain in the butt.

00:07:06.854 --> 00:07:09.693
- No, the only reason
I'm up here

00:07:09.726 --> 00:07:11.162
is to hide from your stench.

00:07:11.195 --> 00:07:14.401
- So what do you think
of my godlike power, hmm?

00:07:14.434 --> 00:07:16.105
Everything my fists touch

00:07:16.139 --> 00:07:18.678
turn into the most amazing fish
you've seen!

00:07:18.711 --> 00:07:20.380
Not to mention my speed,

00:07:20.413 --> 00:07:22.719
along with the unparalleled
flexibility I have

00:07:22.752 --> 00:07:24.388
with this springy body!

00:07:24.422 --> 00:07:26.325
On top of that,
my rippling scales

00:07:26.358 --> 00:07:28.096
allow me to move
without restraint!

00:07:28.129 --> 00:07:30.066
I'm unstoppable!

00:07:31.135 --> 00:07:34.676
I can see you're so terrified,
you're trembling!

00:07:34.709 --> 00:07:38.215
But believe it or not,
I still haven't gotten serious!

00:07:41.256 --> 00:07:42.558
Huh?

00:07:44.762 --> 00:07:47.401
- Even the most jaw-dropping
attack is pointless

00:07:47.434 --> 00:07:48.870
if you can't land it.

00:07:50.874 --> 00:07:54.716
<i>Remember
that boiling fury within me...</i>

00:08:00.761 --> 00:08:04.503
<i>as I watched maggots
infest my beloved brother's body</i>

00:08:04.536 --> 00:08:06.205
<i>as he began to rot.</i>

00:08:07.742 --> 00:08:10.347
<i>I found myself
on the brink of death,</i>

00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:12.885
<i>and the maggots
started feeding on me.</i>

00:08:15.657 --> 00:08:17.829
[drop echoes]

00:08:17.862 --> 00:08:19.666
- Boil some water right away!

00:08:19.700 --> 00:08:22.170
And start applying clean cloth
to their wounds!

00:08:22.203 --> 00:08:23.239
- Yes, Mother!

00:08:25.678 --> 00:08:27.281
[Tokito shudders]

00:08:27.314 --> 00:08:28.551
- [gasps]

00:08:28.584 --> 00:08:30.153
How's the older brother?

00:08:30.186 --> 00:08:31.823
- He passed away before we came.

00:08:31.857 --> 00:08:35.029
- Do everything in your power to
keep the younger brother alive!

00:08:35.062 --> 00:08:36.031
- Yes, Mother!

00:08:36.064 --> 00:08:37.568
[Tokito sighs]

00:08:37.601 --> 00:08:38.571
[water splashes]

00:08:38.604 --> 00:08:40.674
Bro... ther.

00:08:42.277 --> 00:08:43.947
- [gasps]

00:08:43.981 --> 00:08:44.749
- [grunts]

00:08:44.783 --> 00:08:46.986
<i>[foreboding music]</i>

00:08:50.059 --> 00:08:51.128
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:08:51.161 --> 00:08:52.064
[gasps]

00:08:52.097 --> 00:08:55.136
<i>- I was fortunate enough
to be rescued.</i>

00:08:55.169 --> 00:08:56.906
<i>Had I not, I would have died.</i>

00:08:58.076 --> 00:08:59.144
[Tokito grunts]

00:08:59.178 --> 00:09:01.181
[grunting]

00:09:03.520 --> 00:09:06.258
- Lord Tokito,
you're not fully healed yet.

00:09:06.292 --> 00:09:07.293
You shouldn't--

00:09:08.997 --> 00:09:12.972
<i>- I may have lost my memory,
but my body remembers.</i>

00:09:17.549 --> 00:09:20.821
<i>That fury will rage
within me until I die.</i>

00:09:22.992 --> 00:09:26.098
<i>It's how I pushed myself
past my limits,</i>

00:09:26.131 --> 00:09:28.436
<i>how I trained
until I vomited blood.</i>

00:09:28.469 --> 00:09:30.841
<i>To annihilate the demons!</i>

00:09:30.875 --> 00:09:33.847
<i>To put an end to their kind
once and for all.</i>

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:36.219
- Bear witness
to my unbridled strength

00:09:36.252 --> 00:09:38.223
and all its glory!

00:09:38.256 --> 00:09:39.726
Blood Demon Art...

00:09:39.760 --> 00:09:41.830
Killer Fish Scales!

00:09:42.665 --> 00:09:44.101
Hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:09:44.134 --> 00:09:45.337
Now what do you think?

00:09:45.370 --> 00:09:48.710
I doubt you've ever seen
a demon move quite like this!

00:09:48.743 --> 00:09:50.748
My scales allow me
to move at will!

00:09:50.782 --> 00:09:53.086
I'm impossible to predict!

00:09:53.119 --> 00:09:56.425
This speed goes against the laws
of nature, wouldn't you say?

00:09:56.458 --> 00:10:00.200
I wonder what kind of art I
should make out of your body?!

00:10:00.233 --> 00:10:02.705
Maybe I should rip off
that ugly head of yours

00:10:02.738 --> 00:10:05.343
and replace it
with one my lovely fish!

00:10:06.346 --> 00:10:08.683
<i>It's over for you!</i>

00:10:10.955 --> 00:10:13.827
<i>- Mist Breathing
Seventh Form...</i>

00:10:13.861 --> 00:10:15.296
<i>Obscuring Clouds.</i>

00:10:16.900 --> 00:10:17.802
- Huh?

00:10:17.835 --> 00:10:20.642
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:10:20.675 --> 00:10:23.079
<i>No, no, there he is!</i>

00:10:23.112 --> 00:10:24.114
<i>Found him!</i>

00:10:26.018 --> 00:10:27.120
<i>Not there?</i>

00:10:29.559 --> 00:10:30.728
<i>Over there, eh?</i>

00:10:30.761 --> 00:10:33.433
<i>Hyo, hyo! Too slow!</i>

00:10:33.466 --> 00:10:36.906
<i>What's this?
H-How can you vanish?</i>

00:10:38.544 --> 00:10:40.279
<i>What's going on here?</i>

00:10:40.313 --> 00:10:41.817
<i>Where did that brat go?</i>

00:10:41.850 --> 00:10:43.620
<i>It's like-- It's like...</i>

00:10:43.653 --> 00:10:47.361
<i>the area's being
completely shrouded in mist!</i>

00:10:47.394 --> 00:10:50.500
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:10:50.534 --> 00:10:51.736
[gasps]

00:10:52.538 --> 00:10:54.274
- So, tell me.

00:10:54.307 --> 00:10:55.410
- What?

00:10:55.443 --> 00:10:56.880
- What made you think...

00:10:56.913 --> 00:10:58.182
- Huh?

00:10:58.215 --> 00:11:02.223
- ...that you were the only one
not taking this fight seriously?

00:11:05.631 --> 00:11:08.102
[sword rings]

00:11:15.449 --> 00:11:17.888
<i>- What the hell? What the hell?</i>

00:11:17.922 --> 00:11:19.224
<i>Am I upside-down?!</i>

00:11:19.257 --> 00:11:22.832
<i>What's going on here?
Why can't I sense anything?!</i>

00:11:22.865 --> 00:11:25.136
<i>That pest
is finally showing himself!</i>

00:11:25.170 --> 00:11:26.773
<i>I need to make
short work of him</i>

00:11:26.806 --> 00:11:29.077
<i>and report to Lord Muzan!</i>

00:11:33.452 --> 00:11:34.454
<i>Huh?</i>

00:11:35.557 --> 00:11:37.862
<i>B-- B-- Behea--</i>

00:11:37.896 --> 00:11:41.269
<i>Beheaded! Beheaded!
Beheaded! Beheaded!</i>

00:11:41.302 --> 00:11:44.074
<i>Ridiculous! Impossible!
Unbelievable!</i>

00:11:44.108 --> 00:11:46.513
<i>What an unheard-of,
abnormal situation!</i>

00:11:46.546 --> 00:11:48.049
<i>Did I actually lose?</i>

00:11:48.082 --> 00:11:50.788
<i>Me? Lose? I lost to a child?!</i>

00:11:50.822 --> 00:11:53.292
<i>Me, of all people?</i>

00:11:53.326 --> 00:11:54.696
- It's over for you.

00:11:54.729 --> 00:11:55.932
Farewell.

00:11:55.965 --> 00:11:58.903
Do everyone a favor,
and never be reborn again.

00:11:59.705 --> 00:12:01.275
- Curses!

00:12:01.308 --> 00:12:03.480
How could this
have happened to me?!

00:12:03.514 --> 00:12:05.183
A lowly human like you

00:12:05.216 --> 00:12:07.855
shouldn't be able
to decapitate me!

00:12:07.888 --> 00:12:10.561
You abominable,
low-level life-form!

00:12:10.594 --> 00:12:14.769
My life is worth over a hundred
of your wretched kind!

00:12:14.803 --> 00:12:18.042
I am one of the chosen,
exalted life-forms!

00:12:18.075 --> 00:12:20.882
You're nothing but weak flesh
that grows old!

00:12:20.915 --> 00:12:24.288
But I took your insignificant
lives in my hands

00:12:24.321 --> 00:12:28.797
and used those hands to elevate
you all to worthy works of art!

00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:31.268
You ignorant,
vulgar little maggo--

00:12:34.174 --> 00:12:37.380
[slices echo]

00:12:41.789 --> 00:12:43.560
- I've heard more than enough.

00:12:44.461 --> 00:12:47.266
Now go to hell,
where you rightfully belong.

00:12:49.772 --> 00:12:51.843
[wind gusts]

00:12:53.847 --> 00:12:55.718
<i>[wind blowing]</i>

00:12:55.751 --> 00:12:57.053
<i>[sword slices]</i>

00:13:00.861 --> 00:13:02.732
<i>[wind blowing]</i>

00:13:02.765 --> 00:13:04.267
<i>[sword slices]</i>

00:13:05.871 --> 00:13:08.075
[birds chirping]

00:13:12.183 --> 00:13:13.554
- [caws]

00:13:13.587 --> 00:13:16.926
[cawing continues]

00:13:22.070 --> 00:13:23.372
- Try not to be rigid

00:13:23.405 --> 00:13:27.514
about how you perceive
the world around you, Muichiro.

00:13:29.251 --> 00:13:32.658
Once you've rediscovered
your unshakeable self,

00:13:32.691 --> 00:13:35.096
you will become
even more powerful.

00:13:42.377 --> 00:13:45.751
<i>- It's exactly
like the Master said to me.</i>

00:13:45.784 --> 00:13:48.990
<i>As long as I have
my unshakable self,</i>

00:13:49.024 --> 00:13:51.763
<i>I can dig in with both feet
and all my might.</i>

00:13:51.796 --> 00:13:55.604
<i>As long as I know
who I am in my heart,</i>

00:13:55.638 --> 00:13:57.775
<i>all doubt and hesitation</i>

00:13:57.808 --> 00:14:00.180
<i>will disappear like the mist.</i>

00:14:00.213 --> 00:14:03.119
<i>As long as I draw breath,</i>

00:14:03.152 --> 00:14:06.324
<i>no demon on Earth
can escape my blade.</i>

00:14:08.663 --> 00:14:10.901
- Uh, Lord Tokito?

00:14:10.934 --> 00:14:11.903
Lord Tokito!

00:14:11.936 --> 00:14:15.477
Lord Tokito!
You saved our lives!

00:14:15.511 --> 00:14:17.247
But are you all right?

00:14:17.280 --> 00:14:19.451
- Don't worry about me.
I'm fine.

00:14:19.484 --> 00:14:20.954
- Are you sure about that?!

00:14:20.987 --> 00:14:24.228
- Yeah. Why wouldn't I
feel incredible right now?

00:14:24.261 --> 00:14:25.831
- [trembling]
- I should get going.

00:14:25.865 --> 00:14:28.035
I have to join up
with Tanjiro and the others.

00:14:28.069 --> 00:14:29.137
- I don't know.

00:14:29.170 --> 00:14:31.341
You're looking really pale,
Lord Tokito.

00:14:31.374 --> 00:14:33.212
Are you certain
you're all right?

00:14:33.245 --> 00:14:35.884
- Like I said, I'm totally fine.

00:14:35.918 --> 00:14:37.922
What makes you think otherwise?

00:14:37.955 --> 00:14:38.924
[heavy exhale]

00:14:38.957 --> 00:14:41.462
- Huh? I can hear you heaving!

00:14:41.495 --> 00:14:43.701
And I can see
your whole body's trembling!

00:14:43.734 --> 00:14:44.703
- I'm okay.
- Hey, you!

00:14:44.736 --> 00:14:46.105
- But if you don't mind,

00:14:46.138 --> 00:14:48.308
could you go ahead
and check on Kotetsu and...

00:14:49.378 --> 00:14:52.150
- You're literally
frothing at the mouth!

00:14:52.183 --> 00:14:53.219
[shrieks]

00:14:53.252 --> 00:14:54.421
Lord Tokito!

00:14:54.455 --> 00:14:55.456
Oh, crap! Oh, crap!

00:14:55.490 --> 00:14:57.828
Is he about to die?
What am I supposed to do?

00:14:57.861 --> 00:14:59.832
Hey! Somebody!

00:14:59.866 --> 00:15:01.602
- [scraping]
- Mr. Haganezuka!

00:15:03.406 --> 00:15:05.877
Mr. Haganezuka!

00:15:05.911 --> 00:15:07.982
He's not coming to help,
is he?

00:15:08.015 --> 00:15:09.184
I shouldn't be surprised.

00:15:09.217 --> 00:15:11.790
He ignored me
when I was about to be murdered!

00:15:11.823 --> 00:15:13.192
- [retches]

00:15:13.225 --> 00:15:15.196
- Agh!
He's choking on the foam!

00:15:15.230 --> 00:15:18.469
This is bad! Wh-What--
What should I do?

00:15:18.503 --> 00:15:20.907
- You should probably
lay him on his side.

00:15:20.941 --> 00:15:23.245
- Huh? R-Right!

00:15:24.247 --> 00:15:25.249
Huh?!

00:15:26.452 --> 00:15:28.055
[stammers]

00:15:28.857 --> 00:15:30.193
[shrieks]

00:15:30.226 --> 00:15:32.431
It's the ghost
of young Kotetsu!

00:15:32.464 --> 00:15:35.170
- Don't worry. I'm not a ghost.
I'd have to be dead for that.

00:15:35.203 --> 00:15:37.040
- No, they all say that!

00:15:37.073 --> 00:15:38.743
Ghosts are never aware
they're ghosts

00:15:38.777 --> 00:15:40.079
or that they're even dead!

00:15:40.112 --> 00:15:41.749
- Yeah, I know, but I'm alive.

00:15:41.783 --> 00:15:43.219
- No, no, no, no!
Your solar plexus!

00:15:43.252 --> 00:15:44.823
How could you
possibly be alive

00:15:44.856 --> 00:15:46.626
after losing all that blood?

00:15:46.660 --> 00:15:50.266
- Oh, this? This is the blood
from the arm they slashed.

00:15:50.299 --> 00:15:52.203
It must have smeared
on my chest.

00:15:52.237 --> 00:15:54.074
My arm wound's
pretty deep though,

00:15:54.107 --> 00:15:55.376
and if it doesn't stop bleeding,

00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:57.682
then I might
actually be dead soon.

00:15:57.715 --> 00:16:01.188
Oh, yeah, as for my belly...

00:16:01.221 --> 00:16:04.829
that's where I was carrying
the guard Mr. Tanjiro gave me.

00:16:04.862 --> 00:16:05.998
It saved me.

00:16:06.031 --> 00:16:08.335
He specifically said
he wanted it

00:16:08.368 --> 00:16:10.974
to be the guard
on his new sword.

00:16:16.251 --> 00:16:17.253
- Mm!

00:16:18.857 --> 00:16:21.228
Let's give it our all
as Hashira!

00:16:25.169 --> 00:16:27.373
<i>[sentimental music]</i>

00:16:33.185 --> 00:16:37.193
<i>[father] See? Everything
turned out just fine.</i>

00:16:39.932 --> 00:16:41.134
<i>- Father.</i>

00:16:42.738 --> 00:16:44.107
<i>Mother.</i>

00:16:47.413 --> 00:16:48.415
[sighs]

00:16:51.523 --> 00:16:52.658
<i>[Yuichiro] Muichiro...</i>

00:16:52.691 --> 00:17:00.105
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:17:02.712 --> 00:17:04.280
<i>...you did great.</i>

00:17:06.753 --> 00:17:07.755
<i>- Brother.</i>

00:17:07.788 --> 00:17:15.103
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:17:15.136 --> 00:17:16.438
<i>Thank you.</i>

00:17:20.914 --> 00:17:22.350
[whoosh]

00:17:24.922 --> 00:17:26.526
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:17:26.559 --> 00:17:28.362
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:17:28.395 --> 00:17:30.332
<i>- There are
five wooden dragon heads.</i>

00:17:30.366 --> 00:17:33.139
<i>They can expand
to about 66 feet.</i>

00:17:33.172 --> 00:17:35.476
<i>All right!
I've got one thing figured out!</i>

00:17:35.510 --> 00:17:36.478
[drum pounds]

00:17:36.513 --> 00:17:38.048
- [growls]

00:17:38.081 --> 00:17:41.187
<i>- Hinokami Kagura Clear Blue...</i>

00:17:43.058 --> 00:17:45.329
- [high-pitched tone ringing]
- [groans]

00:17:47.935 --> 00:17:49.470
[groans]

00:17:51.743 --> 00:17:52.744
- [grunts]

00:17:55.517 --> 00:17:56.853
- [growls]

00:17:56.886 --> 00:17:58.388
[gun fires]

00:18:00.660 --> 00:18:02.764
[Genya grunting]

00:18:05.670 --> 00:18:06.772
[yells]

00:18:09.344 --> 00:18:10.748
- [gags]

00:18:10.781 --> 00:18:13.753
<i>M-My eardrums just burst!</i>

00:18:13.786 --> 00:18:14.989
<i>I'm so dizzy.</i>

00:18:15.022 --> 00:18:16.124
<i>I can't get up!</i>

00:18:16.157 --> 00:18:17.159
<i>It's no good!</i>

00:18:17.193 --> 00:18:19.666
<i>Get on your feet! Hurry!</i>

00:18:19.699 --> 00:18:21.167
<i>Here comes an attack!</i>

00:18:25.543 --> 00:18:26.779
[yells]

00:18:34.596 --> 00:18:38.168
<i>It can use the powers
of the Four Emotions!</i>

00:18:38.202 --> 00:18:40.774
<i>Not only that,
but the power's been magnified!</i>

00:18:40.808 --> 00:18:42.443
- [grunts]

00:18:42.477 --> 00:18:45.149
- [groans]

00:18:45.183 --> 00:18:47.788
<i>- No time
to use Breathing skills!</i>

00:18:47.822 --> 00:18:49.157
<i>And I can't heal!</i>

00:18:50.661 --> 00:18:52.263
- [growls]

00:18:53.399 --> 00:18:55.771
<i>- I can't handle
the attacks anymore,</i>

00:18:55.804 --> 00:18:57.306
<i>even if I anticipate them!</i>

00:18:59.011 --> 00:19:00.479
<i>I can't catch my breath.</i>

00:19:00.514 --> 00:19:03.720
<i>But if I can somehow
get 66 feet away...</i>

00:19:04.522 --> 00:19:06.659
<i>All right, I can do this!</i>

00:19:08.195 --> 00:19:09.464
- [roars]

00:19:11.335 --> 00:19:12.604
<i>- It's stretching!</i>

00:19:15.109 --> 00:19:16.880
<i>Use a technique!</i>

00:19:16.913 --> 00:19:17.914
<i>Slash it!</i>

00:19:20.119 --> 00:19:21.556
- [gasps]

00:19:21.589 --> 00:19:22.724
- Eh?

00:19:27.768 --> 00:19:30.473
- [roars]

00:19:30.507 --> 00:19:32.511
- [grunting]

00:19:34.848 --> 00:19:36.953
- [yells]

00:19:36.986 --> 00:19:39.190
- [wincing]

00:19:41.863 --> 00:19:43.198
[groans]

00:19:45.002 --> 00:19:46.405
<i>It's hopeless.</i>

00:19:46.438 --> 00:19:47.975
<i>I'm getting crushed.</i>

00:19:48.008 --> 00:19:49.310
[gags]

00:19:53.118 --> 00:19:54.087
[crunch]

00:19:54.120 --> 00:19:56.224
- It's over!

00:19:58.997 --> 00:20:00.466
[blade swishes]

00:20:00.500 --> 00:20:01.636
Hmm?

00:20:01.669 --> 00:20:04.240
<i>[heroic music]</i>

00:20:05.510 --> 00:20:06.713
- [gasps]

00:20:06.746 --> 00:20:12.991
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:20:19.839 --> 00:20:21.341
- A Hashira?

00:20:21.375 --> 00:20:23.613
[Kanroji squeals]

00:20:23.647 --> 00:20:26.352
Such a ghastly monster!
What is that thing?

00:20:26.385 --> 00:20:28.623
- [gasps] Ms. Kanroji?

00:20:28.656 --> 00:20:29.859
- You okay?

00:20:29.892 --> 00:20:31.328
I'm sorry I'm so late!

00:20:31.361 --> 00:20:32.931
That was a close one!

00:20:36.940 --> 00:20:37.908
- [winces]

00:20:37.941 --> 00:20:39.745
Ms. Kanroji!

00:20:40.848 --> 00:20:42.384
- Tanjiro!

00:20:42.417 --> 00:20:44.420
Take a well-deserved break!

00:20:44.454 --> 00:20:45.990
Great job out there!

00:20:46.024 --> 00:20:46.993
I'm proud!

00:20:47.027 --> 00:20:48.262
<i>- I-I can't hear,</i>

00:20:48.295 --> 00:20:50.499
<i>because my eardrums burst.</i>

00:20:51.335 --> 00:20:52.537
- [grunts]

00:20:53.339 --> 00:20:54.541
Tanjiro...

00:20:58.382 --> 00:21:01.454
I promise I'll rescue
Nezuko and Genya, all right?

00:21:03.024 --> 00:21:04.862
- Annoying girl.

00:21:04.896 --> 00:21:06.164
- [grunts]

00:21:06.197 --> 00:21:08.936
So just leave the rest to me!

00:21:10.072 --> 00:21:11.041
- [growls]

00:21:11.074 --> 00:21:13.546
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:21:14.681 --> 00:21:15.951
- W-Wait!

00:21:15.984 --> 00:21:17.654
Upper Rank.

00:21:17.687 --> 00:21:18.690
It's Upper Four!

00:21:18.723 --> 00:21:25.570
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:21:32.049 --> 00:21:33.051
- Hah!

00:21:35.056 --> 00:21:36.759
- [groans]

00:21:39.297 --> 00:21:40.667
- [giggles]

00:21:44.942 --> 00:21:46.913
<i>["Koi Kogare" playing]</i>

00:21:46.946 --> 00:21:53.960
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:23:14.955 --> 00:23:16.526
[page rustles]

00:23:16.559 --> 00:23:18.763
<i>[cheerful music]</i>

00:23:21.936 --> 00:23:25.577
<i>[Zenitsu] What gives?
When's our turn?</i>

00:23:25.610 --> 00:23:28.415
Hey, you, when's my turn?

00:23:28.448 --> 00:23:29.585
- Huh? Huh?

00:23:29.618 --> 00:23:32.625
I can't detect
any traces of the enemy!

00:23:32.658 --> 00:23:34.160
Where the heck is the enemy?

00:23:34.193 --> 00:23:37.300
- Nowhere, 'cause our turn
isn't happening for a while!

00:23:37.333 --> 00:23:38.301
- Huh?

00:23:38.335 --> 00:23:39.605
- Oh, boy.

00:23:39.638 --> 00:23:41.341
We're gonna
carry out this mission,

00:23:41.374 --> 00:23:43.211
then move on to the next one.

00:23:43.245 --> 00:23:44.447
Next, Episode 10,

00:23:44.480 --> 00:23:46.719
"Love Hashira, Mitsuri Kanroji."

00:23:46.753 --> 00:23:49.190
- You better demolish
that Upper Rank demon!

00:23:49.223 --> 00:23:51.494
You got that, Senpachiro?

